    <body>
        <h2>InTouch screen does not properly fit display</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>This is usually a TV settings issue and the fix is dependent on the TV's manufacturer. </li>
            <li>In most instances, change the Aspect Ratio to “Just Scan” from the TV's menu or cycle through available TV Aspect Ratio options to find the most suitable one.</li>
        </ul>
    </body>
</html>